{"type":null,"faqId":49747,"title":"华为智能手表_手表支持心率检测吗？如何使用？","answer":"<body style=\"clear:both; padding-left:10px; padding-top:5px; padding-right:5px; padding-bottom:5px\"><div id=\"body7571935\"><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329148__p35821310\">支持静态心率检测。</p><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329148__p541926881833\">检测心率时请保证手表正面向上，心率检测区域贴合到手腕上，最好轻按手表表面增加与手腕的贴合度。检测过程中保持手腕水平不动，这样便于您获取更准确的检测数据。</p><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329148__p391922931834\"><span><img src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/b0666_hsrrc.png\" height=\"232.61700000000002\" width=\"399\" title=\"点击放大\" class=\"imgResize\"></span></p><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329148__p5655978918736\">在手表主界面向左滑动一下，点击  <span><img src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/b0667_ttdon.png\" width=\"26.63325\" height=\"26.63325\" title=\"点击放大\" class=\"imgResize\"></span> <strong id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329148__b88691721885\">心率</strong>，根据界面提示允许心率访问传感器数据，开始检测。</p><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329148__p3927605418736\">点击 <strong id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329148__b6103388618811\">再次测量</strong> 可进行多次测量获取更准确的心率数据。</p><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329148__p2724381118736\"><span><img src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/b0668_1fra9.png\" height=\"123.29100000000001\" width=\"399\" title=\"点击放大\" class=\"imgResize\"></span></p><div class=\"note\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329148__note609413718947\"><img src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/b0669_fahwm.gif\"><span class=\"notetitle\"> 说明： </span><div class=\"notebody\"><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329148__p5484723718947\">检测结果不作为医学参考。</p></div></div><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329148__p3254643511411\">感谢您支持并使用华为手表，关于手表心率监测的更多信息，请您在Wi-Fi环境下参阅视频教程：<a href=\"http://v.youku.com/v_show/id_XMTQyODE1NzEwOA==.html\" target=\"_blank\">http://v.youku.com/v_show/id_XMTQyODE1NzEwOA==.html</a></p></div><div></div></body>","faqTypeId":211,"faqType":"运动及健康监测","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"zh-cn_topic_0022329148","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Sports-Health-Monitoring","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":nu